{"tid":809186,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"3DMark實錘華為手機作弊 P20與Nova 3紛紛上榜","createTime":"2018-09-07T03:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T15:37:17.000Z","uid":10717,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"adf50f822616e095b190138373379bf8f7a62312","tid":809186,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"3DMark母公司UL Benchmark今天正式對華為P20 Pro、華為Nova 3和榮耀Play三款手機的3DMark測試分數提出了質疑，三款手機違反了UL Benchmark的測試準則，存在自動識別跑分軟件，刻意提升性能情況。並宣佈將華為P20 Pro、華為Nova 3和榮耀Play設備從設備性能排行榜單中除名。<br />\n<br />\n        隨後UL Benchmark又根據著名測試媒體Anandtech測試報告，還取消了華為P20的測試分數。這意味著華為近半年推出的4款手機新品紛紛被逐出3DMark性能排行版。<br />\n<br />\n　　對於逐榜理由，UL Benchmark認為在3DMark測試中，以上華為四款手機，在公共版本的3DMark測試分數部分，遠遠高出了UL內部版、不帶識別特徵的3DMark測試數據，數值增幅達到47%左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/07/112016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2F112016_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=078c7b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑色為公共版本3DMark分數，橙色為內部版本3DMark分數<br />\nUL Benchmark懷疑這些設備通過識別3DMark應用程式，從而通過特殊手段獲取高分，並不能適應日常應用。這套做法在3DMark的準則中被明令禁止，硬件性能優化必須具備普遍適用性，而不能僅針對個別程式。<br />\n<br />\n　　目前華為已經承認了UL Benchmark的質疑，並承諾在未來更新中會使用更透明的測試解決方案。同時華為還會向普通用戶提供性能模式的訪問權限，確保用戶在有必要時獲得設備的最大性能。<br />\n       3DMark規範向來以變態出名，他們15年前就透過向高規格合作媒體提供開發者版本。媒體藉此發現英偉達的NV30驅動存在軌跡預記錄回放、渲染精度縮水等非普適性優化，英偉達在當時被搞得焦頭爛額，受到業界狂轟濫炸，英偉達從此對驅動團隊進行了大力整頓，製定了驅動優化原則：廣譜。直到NV40發佈後，英偉達才從NV30的陰影徹底走出來，再無發生類似問題。<br />\n<br />\n原文鏈接:<a href=\"https://techreport.com/news/3407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechreport.com%2Fnews%2F3407&d=Lef8AG442bpl9RNJhf0oppnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=3f01b2a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://techreport.com/news/3407</a> ... heating-revelations<br />\n<br />\n華為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1770e86bb97aade77644b5285fecc866d4a24d0","tid":809186,"uid":20890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"支那狗真係呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4085c8310fd255674a6e49f03dde08eb14f8c5fd","tid":809186,"uid":194130,"like":2,"dislike":38,"score":-36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"其實個個都咁做<br />\n不過係大陸做假都冇用腦太明顯比人捉到<br />\n好心啦做假都用下個腦啦"},{"pid":"1bdc7c672eafb9f9866e2468d74197c92313507f","tid":809186,"uid":19012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:14:19.000Z","msg":"連跑分都要造假<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0a66593f2a06e4ef51ee93b1fd1ccb09706672","tid":809186,"uid":6680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73903fe12c399a2cfe3bb88f0a70f37397528832","tid":809186,"uid":164092,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"Sony嘅QC 3.0算唔算做假？"},{"pid":"5f4ca2d580c4446dad01f3fd312af6bd98529d83","tid":809186,"uid":109780,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"不過nova3真係抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b5a718110ffb46dcf59bddb1db4b69516ad1c2","tid":809186,"uid":78304,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:15:57.000Z","msg":"對比起部機用既餡, 跑分出貓只係冰山一角"},{"pid":"b466028a138db6f27f6a081d3be6ff6b43fc943b","tid":809186,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"屎為除左影相有啲睇頭外，真係由裡到外，hardware 同software 都係垃圾"},{"pid":"8a3a54ba3fcf6f9ec0ef7de77cf519789bed15d2","tid":809186,"uid":10717,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quo